  "general_provisions": "This bill addresses pregnancy and infant loss.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>recognizes October as Pregnancy and Infant Loss Awareness Month;<hr><ltbullet>requires the Division of Licensing and Background Checks, with the Office of Maternal and Child Health, to establish rules and procedures for a health care facility that provides birthing services when an individual experiences a pregnancy or infant loss; and<hr><ltbullet>requires the Division of Professional Licensing, with the Department of Health and Human Services, to develop a training for certain health care professionals on supporting an individual experiencing a pregnancy or infant loss.",
